	<Title>
		Sleep aids: Could antihistamines help me sleep?
	</Title>
	<Abstract>
		Antihistamines are somewhat effective as sleep aids &amp;mdash; but only for occasional insomnia.
	</Abstract>
	<Question>
		Is it OK to use over-the-counter antihistamines to treat insomnia? I&apos;d like to avoid prescription sleep aids.
	</Question>
